1. The "turf" is titled a "water feature" in the floor plan. I was really hoping it was a Japanese footbath a la Bay Hotel Ginza from the capsule hotel video. That would have been a nice dovetail. Alas: Astroturf.

2. That hotel suite has not been reserviced since approximately 2004. Hence the excess decor and lack of modern technology (retractable tv's, old office phone.) Refreshed, probably - new linen, replaced carpet, new beds, flat screen TVs, but nothing major. It's not quite old enough to be "vintage" but give it another 20 years.

3. Tori Amos plays Bosendorfer pianos!

4. So. Many. Horses.

5. I hope the hot tub was working when you were actually staying there! It looks AMAZING!
